___
> ## Brown Bear
>*Large beast, unaligned*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 11 (natural armor)
> - **Hit Points** 34 (4d10 + 12)
> - **Speed** 40 ft., climb 30 ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|19 (+4)|10 (+0)|16 (+3)|2 (-4)|13 (+1)|7 (-2)|
>___
> - **Skills** Perception +3
> - **Senses** passive Perception 13
> - **Languages** None
> - **Challenge** 1 (200 XP)
> ___
> ***Keen Smell. *** The bear has advantage on Wisdom(Perception) checks that rely on smell.
>
> ### Actions
> ***Multiattack.*** The bear makes two attacks with its bite and claws.

> ***Bite.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +5 to hit, reach 5ft., one target. *Hit:* 8 (1d8 + 4) piercing damage.

> ***Claws.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +5 to hit, reach 5ft., one target. *Hit:* 11 (2d6 + 4) slashing damage.